Moffett says revenue per megabyte of wireless to drop: Audio

-- B y  
-- 
2011-03-25T20:12:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-25/moffett-says-revenue-per-megabyte-of-wireless-to-drop-audio.html
Craig Moffett , Vice President of Sanford
C Bernstein and Company, says that revenue per megabyte of 
wireless data will fall to 3 cents by 2014. Moffett, speaking on
the Hays Advantage on Bloomberg Radio, says the current number 
is 46 cents.    (Source: Bloomberg)  Running time 21:36  -0- Mar/25/2011 20:12 GMT
 